UID:10029554-1774890000-1774897200@www.phinneycenter.org
SUMMARY:Spring Refresh featuring Screen Printing!
DESCRIPTION:Spring Refresh: A Screen Printing Party and Clothing Drive  \nCome connect!\nJoin us for Spring Refresh\, a hands-on event where neighbors come together to create\, give\, and care for one another. This evening is both a fun activity and an opportunity to show up for our community!  \nScreen Printing! \nBring a piece of light colored clothing to participate in screen-printing fun. PNA’s amazing Woodshop built two custom screen-printing presses for the night. (We will also have white t-shirts available for sale.) \nChoose from two designs: \nThe iconic PhinneyWood Heart – A bold\, graphic symbol of neighborhood pride and love for local small businesses.\nThe PNA Orca\, designed by PNA Art Club member Chino – A powerful symbol of shared knowledge\, care across generations\, and community traditions. \nLet’s wear our values and tell the story of a community that shows up for one another. \nSpring Clothing Drive for the Hot Meal Program \nAs we gather\, we’ll also be collecting clean\, lightly worn clothing for adults to support the PNA’s Hot Meal Program Community Closet. Men’s clothing is especially needed. Some of our most requested items include: \n\nNew socks and underwear\nLightly used shoes and boots\nMen’s pants\, especially larger sizes\n\nLast year\, the Hot Meal Program served over 21\,000 free meals\, while also connecting neighbors to medical care\, haircuts\, and essential resources.\nThanks to you\, this support is possible. When you bring clothing or donate\, you’re directly helping meet real needs in our neighborhood. \nTunes\, Snacks & Lemonade \nEnjoy music\, light snacks\, and refreshing lemonade while you print\, connect\, and give back. \nWho’s Invited \nYou!\nThis all-ages event is open to neighbors\, PNA Members\, local PhinneyWood small business owners\, and anyone curious about the PNA. Come meet your neighbors\, learn what’s happening\, and be part of something meaningful. \nEvent Details \nMonday\, March 30\n5:00–7:00 pm\nPhinney Center – Room 7\n6532 Phinney Ave N\, Seattle\, WA 98103  \nFree for members \n$10 for non-members \nDonations welcome to support the PNA programs such as the Hot Meal Program.  \nSpots are limited—register soon to reserve yours! \n  \nRSVP
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/screen-printing-party/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus\, 6532 Phinney Ave. N.\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103\, United States
CATEGORIES:Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://media.phinneycenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/02112405/PXL_20250613_002316361-e1767381931681.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="PNA Members":MAILTO:membership@phinneycenter.org
END:VEVENT
