SUMMARY:Spring Craft Class: Rock Painting
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, March 31. GSC. Free class. $6 Material Fee. \nPainting rocks is easy and surprisingly fun. Make a garden marker\, a paperweight\, an inspirational gift – so versatile! Includes a sheet of design ideas intended to help even the most entry-level painter feel artistic. If you can hold a pen\, you can paint a rock! Registration required: 206.297.0875\, or arielb@phinneycenter.org. \n 
