SUMMARY:Vital Sculpt HIIT Class with Seattle Jazzercise
DESCRIPTION:Phinney Center\, Blue Building\, Room 7: This invigorating HIIT-style exercise class promotes strength\, vitality\, and long-term hormone health with a science-backed blend of targeted sculpting\, high-intensity cardio\, and functional movement training. This is a group fitness class. Please bring a water bottle and an optional sweat towel. All other equipment will be provided. \nVital Sculpt HIIT meets every Tuesday at 5:30 pm at the Phinney Center.
